ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b2ff8f412fe957127a7bea455e969bd3b4d15c","tid":2491794,"uid":22210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3887c7e1b393850804024f34e74be5d33f03bef0","tid":2491794,"uid":67518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe6b770deefea3ad99b5ddb68d0f6458e5f3bce1","tid":2491794,"uid":22210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"有冇戴口罩咁影？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:37:45.000Z","msg":"有呀，叫做好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但都好可疑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知佢用嚟做乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:38:48.000Z","msg":"[注意!!] 尖沙咀有一班中年呀姐呀叔係咁偷拍同搵人自拍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aNcmMbV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aNcmMbV</a><br />\n#68 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能真係呢單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5d10d45eee6b05f88a3aea04a79602b2292f28","tid":2491794,"uid":15195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNeYy46dwuy2gncfL5Q3KuVsTnAuC9dWf2YFmxt8oFfd7?filename=ZDL5CHN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZDL5CHN.jpg&h=9d328eaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港昨日迎來國安法實施後首個「全民國家安全教育日」，全港各區舉辦了形式多樣、豐富多彩的活動。「全民國安．家安．同心匯─全民同心大拼圖活動」昨日在港島、九龍、新界三個會場同步進行，吸引大批市民參加，各區會場都一度出現排隊人龍。市民或自選照片或現場自拍，紛紛留下今屆「全民國家安全教育日」的個人專屬回憶，更希望透過活動，表達眾人同心一致維護國家安全、守護美好家園的願景。由市民照片拼接而成的「同心匯」拼圖壁，活動結束後將移師添馬公園展覽。\\大公報記者 李亞清、許詠妍、解雪薇（文、圖）<br />\n<br />\nfrom 大公<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.takungpao.com.hk/news/232109/2021/0416/574975.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.takungpao.com.hk%2Fnews%2F232109%2F2021%2F0416%2F574975.html&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLWaNvfBTe1yd